                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ронова",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Ruler of Death, under whose leadership the Night Kingdom was created and the rules of Natlan were established. It is believed that she greatly exceeded her authority as a shade, and this angered the Heavenly Principles.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Using the divine throne of Natlan allows one to use the power of Ronova, and the price for this power is death.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
